As of the latest update:
• Normal service: ~ PKR 400, processing ~15 working days. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}
• Urgent: ~ PKR 1,150, around 12 working days. :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
• Executive: ~ PKR 2,150, about 6 working days. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}

Required documents usually include:
1. Original CNIC (if renewing) / B-Form or birth certificate (for first time). :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}
2. CNIC copy of a parent or blood relative for verification. :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}
3. Proof of identity/address if asked. Sometimes old CNIC, passport, or domicile certificate. :contentReference[oaicite:7]{index=7}
4. In case of lost/damaged card: FIR or affidavit. :contentReference[oaicite:8]{index=8}
